<br />
Kill him first and worry about dying some other day.  Assume you have a cleric on the fight and the cleric is going to live.  If you go in with less than certain numbers the last thing you want to do is hold yourself back and reduce your chances of winning.  If you want a safety valve, take a necro and have them feign.  The best advice is to take overwhelming force. Seriously, the hard part is getting you and the UDB into the same room at the same time.  Take enough troops to make sure you don't have to do it twice.</span></td>
